body.description:
Define the abstract BaseDevice class that every rack component must implement. This is the foundation — everything else inherits from it.

Problem: The rack's uniform interface requires every device to implement the same contract. Without a concrete abstract base, nothing enforces it at import time.

Proposed shape:
- agent_datacenter/device.py:
  from abc import ABC, abstractmethod
  class BaseDevice(ABC):
    @abstractmethod
    def who_am_i(self) -> dict: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def requirements(self) -> dict: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def capabilities(self) -> dict: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def comms(self) -> dict: ...  # read_only/write_only/read_write; Push/Pull/Nudge flags
    @abstractmethod
    def interface_version(self) -> str: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def health(self) -> dict: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def uptime(self) -> float: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def startup_errors(self) -> list: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def logs(self) -> dict: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def update_info(self) -> dict: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def where_and_how(self) -> dict: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def restart(self) -> None: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def block(self, reason: str) -> None: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def halt(self) -> None: ...
    @abstractmethod
    def recovery(self) -> None: ...
  INTERFACE_VERSION = '1.0'

Affected files:
- ~/dev/src/agent_datacenter/agent_datacenter/device.py

Design rules:
- oop-first: ABC with abstractmethod decorators — subclasses that miss any method raise TypeError at import time, not at runtime
- docs-in-code: module docstring describes the rack contract model; each method has a one-line docstring stating its return shape

Scope boundary:
IN: abstract base class only, INTERFACE_VERSION constant
OUT: any concrete device implementations (those are Phase 1 Postgres + Phase 2 Igor tickets)

Test plan:
- Class that inherits BaseDevice but doesn't implement health() raises TypeError when instantiated
- INTERFACE_VERSION is importable as agent_datacenter.device.INTERFACE_VERSION
- All 16 abstract methods present and named per spec
